high_descs: Turn left to go to the shelf, to the right of the book case.
Pick up the pencil on the lower shelf.
Turn right, to face the desk.
Put the pencil in the mug that is nearest to the chair.
Pick up the mug with the pencil in it.
Turn around to return to the shelf, to the right of the book case.
Place the mug on the bottom shelf, to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pencil in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the low cabinet to the right of the bookshelf.
Pick up the pencil from the opening in the cabinet.
Turn right to face the desk.
Drop the pencil, sharpened end up, into the mug nearest the desk chair.
Pick up the mug with the pencil in it.
Return to the low cabinet to the right of the bookshelf.
Put the mug holding the pencil into the left end of the opening in the cabinet, near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug holding a pencil into an open cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to your left and move towards the drawer beside the book shelf
Pick up the pencil on the drawer
Turn to your right face the desk
Put the pencil in the mug closer to the lamp
Pick up the mug with pencil
Turn around to your right and face the drawer beside the book shelf
Put the mug with pencil on drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with pencil on the drawer

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the small table
Pick up a pencil off of the table
Turn directly to your right
Put the pencil in the mug that is sitting on the desk
Pick up the mug with the pencil in it
Head back to the small table you originally got the pencil from
Put the mug with the pencil on it on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with the pencil on it on a shelf

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the small black end table that is between the tall book shelf and the desk.
Pick up the pencil that is on the shelf, below the top of the black end table.
Turn to your right so that you are facing the desk.
Place the pencil in the coffee cup that is directly in front of the office chair.
Pick up the coffee cup on the desk, containing the pencil.
Turn back to your left so that you are facing the end table again.
Place the coffee cup containing the pencil, on the shelf of the end table, between the top and the base.
anns.task_desc: Place a coffee cup containing a pencil on the shelf of the end table, to the left of the desk.
